{"timestamp":"2026-05-19T10:19:57.393Z","taskId":"KB-005","text":" \"take the first entry.\" This is fine but slightly imprecise — it should maybe be more explicit about using `entries[0]` or similar.\n\n2. **The `<Content />` component**: The spec says to use `<Content />` component from Astro's content collections. In Astro 5, when you get an entry from a collection with glob loader, the entry has a `Content`","type":"thinking","agent":"reviewer"}
